data.text:
The Directorate of Transferable Skills and Leadership Development pleased to inform that the Literary Club of RUAS is celebrating the timeless literary art of Gurudev Rabindranath Tagore .

A platform for all of us at RUAS to celebrate ​‘uThe Timeless Art’ is being provided by ​‘The Literary Clb’. No language barrier and no judgement .Just participate and present your favorite form of literary art in your unique elegant style.

This event will be held in both the campuses on below mentioned schedule.

“The Literary Art of Rabindranath Tagore”.

Event Details — RTC:

Date : 02 May ​‚2024

Time : 2 pm to 5 pm

Venue : A206, RTC — Peenya .

Event Details — GG :

Date : 03 May,2024

Venue: Gurukul, FDS — GG Campus.
